{"tid":1605143,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"請緊記: 黑警唔係MMA選手或軍人，面罩下既佢地係好普通既人","createTime":"2019-09-30T07:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T09:52:08.000Z","uid":161430,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cddc5fdde0add785cf8edc54c2a183a70cd12100","tid":1605143,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:46:42.000Z","msg":"每每速龍、防暴一衝出黎果時，你見佢套制服，知佢警察<br />\n係咪好撚恐怖呢？<span style=\"color: red;\">一見佢地full gear身影都怯一怯</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20190619/s00006/37234acfc6c927a8692c8f3b855b130b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20190619%2Fs00006%2F37234acfc6c927a8692c8f3b855b130b.jpg&h=62a8baf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://farm4.staticflickr.com/3931/15233205147_45e6db6419.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm4.staticflickr.com%2F3931%2F15233205147_45e6db6419.jpg&h=0ce76df9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都係，我見到都淆，但其實有時更加淆係成個環境，<br />\n佢地一衝，好多人又第一時間雞飛狗走，<br />\n第一個走，其他人又跟住走，現場好似喪屍片走難<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">久而久之，形成一種強烈感覺:<br />\n佢地一出場就恐撚怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n但幻想下，如果喺條街見到下圖呢種樣貌既市民，你有何恐懼？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MwHxrHK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMwHxrHK.png&h=88681909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/uFMFr0V.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地甚至係望落弱過你好多既，毫無威勢既人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/8OMnP0Q.png\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LAnKwSy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLAnKwSy.jpg&h=86b6d27e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>全部gear同mask背後，呢班人只係好普通好普通既人</strong></span>"},{"pid":"8588c1932cfe0127eae8a62f4542b9ed494d782b","tid":1605143,"uid":161430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:47:07.000Z","msg":"可能你會心諗成個post都講緊廢話，屌，鬼唔知阿媽係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但只係想全部人自己趁有時間，做多次心理輔導同預備，<br />\n其實你恐懼緊既人，就係上圖既普通人，<br />\n你一直恐懼既，係佢地果種身份同形象，<br />\n而唔係呢個人真係有乜咁勁。<br />\n<br />\n就好似好細個時，覺得有d miss阿sir好惡，好驚佢，<br />\n大過諗返，條撚樣只係喺度玩細路，係普通阿叔阿嬸一名。<br />\n大過後喺街見返佢，直頭藐鳩佢。<br />\n<br />\n所以你最後一定可以慢慢克服對速龍、防暴等既恐懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係人多過佢地好多既時候，更加絕對克服倒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbe0266e220d1aa4927e829e9a7e9f9d92a0e92","tid":1605143,"uid":6165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"一向都話黑警無左件制服<br />\n根本係一件垃圾"},{"pid":"d98f3059e25732e1a86218593b41dbfe7f480a9e","tid":1605143,"uid":161430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://buzznews.news/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/TEMPTEMP-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-2-1024x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbuzznews.news%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2FTEMPTEMP-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25BE%25A9-2-1024x576.jpg&h=00633e78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c685c1af9fbc32dc5d3ad32ec1f2fb3d97fc487","tid":1605143,"uid":279689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s